4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience who wish to become cybersecurity specialists. This 16-week program includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will gain knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop